ComicInfo.Summary: A Crypt Called Ithaca [Part 3]: Kirk pursues Gary Seven across time to prevent Seven from killing Kirk in the past. Meanwhile, Spock leads the Enterprise to defend the Federation against the Tholians, with Bright Eyes attempting to convince his fellow Tholians to call off their attack.
